PAID IN FULL Choices & Consequences
Inspired by the true story behind the film Paid in Full, this piece reflects
a moment in history where ambition, survival, and circumstance
collided. The story highlights how environment, opportunity, and
decisions shape outcomes reminding us that fast money often comes
with long-term costs.
This artwork isnt about glorifying the hustle, but about understanding
the lessons: the importance of ownership, foresight, and choosing paths
that build lasting success rather than temporary wins.
Culture Note: Real wealth is freedom, not fast money.
